p.k: Starfire is visited by three ghosts and shown the true meaning of Black Friday. / The Titans learn about cartoon-style violence in order to get revenge on a snack-stealing squirrel. / Robin makes the other Titans sell their treasured mementos from past episodes. / The Titans (except Beast Boy) are cursed on St. Patrick's Day and must travel to the end of the rainbow for the cure. / When Cyborg starts to rage out, Starfire takes him to her secret garden in the backyard to relax.
